ARTICLE 1 — PURPOSE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

This license allows developers, researchers, and integrators to
freely access the NeoKube software to discover, learn, experiment,
and contribute, while reserving commercial production usage for
Neomnia Studio's contractual framework.

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
ARTICLE 2 — DEFINITIONS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

"Software" means any source code, configuration, agent, workflow,
documentation, and resource published in this repository under the
NeoKube Community brand, developed by Neomnia Studio.

"Permitted Use" means any use for:
  - academic or personal research;
  - local development and experimentation;
  - internal demonstration or non-billed proof of concept (POC);
  - open contribution to this repository.

"Prohibited Use" means any deployment or usage generating direct
or indirect revenue, or exposed to end users in production
conditions (see Article 4).

