  b) Any integration into a SaaS service, business application, or
     automated workflow with a commercial purpose;
  c) Any resale, commercial redistribution, or sublicensing to a
     third party;
  d) Any use in the context of a billed service engagement.

To move to production, contact:
  → commercial@neomnia.net
  → https://neomnia.net

